Title: Secop and Official Distributor Prima Prospek at RHVAC Indonesia 2025
Summary: Secop, a global leader in refrigeration technologies, announces its participation at RHVAC Indonesia 2025 together with its local partner Prima Prospek, the official distributor in the region. From September 24 to 26, 2025, at the Jakarta International Expo, booth AQ-01, Secop will showcase its latest sustainable and efficient refrigeration solutions.
